# Reference Class Data Property Extensions
# Note: Spec 미정의 9건 삭제 (location, startDate, endDate, isVirtual,
#       companyId, email, wiTitle, specType, groupId) - 2026-02-13
# Note: meetingId 제거됨 (meetingNumber와 중복, Spec에 없음) - 2026-02-05
